{"tid":2254952,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓流感疫苗奪27命 專家籲停接種","createTime":"2020-10-23T07:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T04:31:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e0f759b12ad5e19c4e5514c45ca56ab8e0c802ca","tid":2254952,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:52:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201023/BU6MQTNV7JESHPZ2JQOSL4H2IA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201023%2FBU6MQTNV7JESHPZ2JQOSL4H2IA%2F&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FREkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=e89da325\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201023%2FBU6MQTNV7JESHPZ2JQOSL4H2IA%2F&h=817efb7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201023/BU6MQTNV7JESHPZ2JQOSL4H2IA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n南韓流感疫苗奪27命 專家籲停接種<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IkzhxXAj-u_AAVxhZ_KNVxYLeVk=/1316x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4NUVNIAMNVGJDA4UTYHZ4XGB7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIkzhxXAj-u_AAVxhZ_KNVxYLeVk%3D%2F1316x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4NUVNIAMNVGJDA4UTYHZ4XGB7E.jpg&h=0335cbf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■研究團隊表示會繼續疫苗臨床實驗。法新社<br />\n<br />\n南韓截至昨午已有至少27人在接種流感疫苗後死亡，。。。。。。。。。。。，疫苗導致死亡的可能性極低。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武肺疫苗志願者死亡<br />\n<br />\n死亡個案中，至少兩宗死因初步判斷可能是過敏性休克，而當局前日指調查六宗死亡個案後發現與疫苗沒直接關係；疫苗中沒有毒物質，當中五人本身有健康問題。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。另外，巴西衞生局前日指一名參與俗稱「牛津疫苗」的武漢肺炎疫苗臨床試驗的志願者死亡，是全球首位。<br />\n<br />\n該疫苗由英國牛津大學和阿斯利康藥廠共同研發。牛津大學證實測試會繼續，發聲明指經過謹慎評估後，認為「臨床試驗沒有安全隱憂」。協助進行第三期試驗的聖保羅聯邦大學指至今已有8,000志願者獲注射試劑。據報死者是28歲的男醫生，死於武肺併發症，又指他屬試驗中的對照群組，注射的是安慰劑。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"a7bddf2363fc2bc80ecf3eff3f32442c7311bb07","tid":2254952,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:54:04.000Z","msg":"泡菜發生咗D咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489e77b1ce04b6978299fdcc8f0f48e38a243814","tid":2254952,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:54:25.000Z","msg":"其實香港都有，不過冇報導之嘛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689b0a4e64b37a568affd3656dcc533a5d635081","tid":2254952,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"489e77b1ce04b6978299fdcc8f0f48e38a243814","tid":2254952,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:54:25.000Z","msg":"其實香港都有，不過冇報導之嘛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:56:48.000Z","msg":"香港啲針唔係喺南韓入口/同南韓同一批次<br />\n不過老人家係易過後生仔有併發症"},{"pid":"ad6773827d166821592f5ad98e748fa16c225c9b","tid":2254952,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:57:58.000Z","msg":"好似已經打左1300萬人"},{"pid":"e1455e53a3c8f4eb918e228a2a5aa9907376c1b6","tid":2254952,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"689b0a4e64b37a568affd3656dcc533a5d635081","tid":2254952,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"489e77b1ce04b6978299fdcc8f0f48e38a243814","tid":2254952,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:54:25.000Z","msg":"其實香港都有，不過冇報導之嘛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T07:56:48.000Z","msg":"香港啲針唔係喺南韓入口/同南韓同一批次<br />\n不過老人家係易過後生仔有併發症"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T08:04:13.000Z","msg":"後生本身就有抵抗流感既能力未必會打， 老人家打又驚有併發症。"},{"pid":"9d8ca8048ea448107c26cf18e419b0a71694ea79","tid":2254952,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T04:31:03.000Z","msg":"韓奪命流感針 衞署改口認有引入<br />\n- 分享自 LIHK